                            <comment id="53566" author="joshua" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2013 20:57:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=adilger&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;adilger&quot;&gt;adilger&lt;/a&gt; Richard did confirm he had his @intel.com address in Gerrit. I did not think to ask him to look at his git log.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53565" author="adilger" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2013 20:42:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Richard, is it possible that there is some patch that isn&apos;t from you on the branch you are trying to push?  It might be that there is an earlier uncommitted patch from someone else that Gerrit is complaining about?  What does &quot;git log&quot; show?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The other potential problem is if you are pushing with &quot;richard.henwood@intel.com&quot; but this email is not registered to your account (maybe only your @whamcloud.com address)?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="53563" author="rhenwood" created="Thu, 7 Mar 2013 20:38:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Refreshing my clone fixed this problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
